| Relationship Type | Classes Involved             | Description                    |
| ----------------- | ---------------------------- | ------------------------------ |
| Inheritance       | Administrator → User         | Admin is a User                |
| Inheritance       | HospitalStaff → User         | Hospital staff is a User       |
| Inheritance       | AuthorizedStaff → User       | Staff is a User                |
| Association       | HospitalStaff ↔ BloodRequest | Requests blood                 |
| Association       | Administrator ↔ BloodRequest | Approves/rejects requests      |
| Association       | User ↔ Notification          | Receives notifications         |
| Aggregation       | BloodInventory ◇ BloodUnit   | Inventory contains blood units |
| Aggregation       | Report ◇ System Data         | Reports aggregate system data  |
